WEBVTT

00:13.830 --> 00:14.910
Your Highness, you asked me to keep an eye

00:14.910 --> 00:16.960
on news about
Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

00:16.960 --> 00:18.820
Guess what happened? Overnight,

00:19.030 --> 00:20.600
Jiabao Restaurant
and Yong'an Pavilion both

00:20.600 --> 00:23.030
started to have people tell stories about
Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

00:23.030 --> 00:24.360
I felt something was fishy.

00:24.360 --> 00:25.870
It was only later that I learned

00:25.870 --> 00:27.600
Chef He Wu of Jiabao Restaurant

00:27.800 --> 00:30.260
and Accountant He An
of Yong'an Pavilion are

00:30.280 --> 00:32.200
both Eunuch He's sworn brothers.

00:32.390 --> 00:33.880
You even know about

00:33.880 --> 00:35.340
their sworn brotherhood?

00:35.350 --> 00:36.240
Cats have their ways,

00:36.240 --> 00:37.440
and dogs have theirs.

00:37.560 --> 00:39.400
Not only do I know
that they are sworn brothers,

00:39.400 --> 00:40.750
but I also know that Eunuch He

00:40.750 --> 00:42.200
gained the Empress Dowager's trust

00:42.200 --> 00:44.320
because before Empress Dowager He
entered the imperial palace,

00:44.320 --> 00:45.000
her wet nurse

00:45.000 --> 00:46.880
and the mother
of the second daughter-in-law

00:46.880 --> 00:48.200
of Eunuch He's seventh uncle

00:48.200 --> 00:49.280
are cousins.

00:49.920 --> 00:51.670
There is a lot of such news in Jiankang

00:51.670 --> 00:52.840
that only someone like me

00:52.840 --> 00:53.750
can find out.

00:53.750 --> 00:54.790
Otherwise, why...

00:54.790 --> 00:56.720
Why would His Highness recruit me?

00:57.560 --> 00:58.690
I'm taking my leave.

01:01.750 --> 01:04.480
The Directorate of Armaments,
Prince Changsha,

01:05.710 --> 01:07.840
Xie Huaigui, and the Empress Dowager.

01:08.240 --> 01:10.000
The battle back on Jiuzhang Plain

01:10.000 --> 01:11.930
was jointly orchestrated by them.

01:12.280 --> 01:13.760
Since the Empress Dowager dared
to push Young Master

01:13.760 --> 01:15.160
of Miraculous Craft into the storm,

01:15.160 --> 01:16.120
she must have cut off

01:16.120 --> 01:18.120
all her connections to this matter.

01:21.640 --> 01:22.840
The fake Xiao Sheng is

01:23.560 --> 01:24.890
probably already dead.

01:25.789 --> 01:27.400
I wrongly blamed Young Master Yao.

01:27.400 --> 01:29.280
This fallout won't reach
the Empress Dowager.

01:29.280 --> 01:31.310
At most, Xie Huaigui will take the fall.

01:31.310 --> 01:32.789
It's killing two birds
with one stone anyway.

01:32.789 --> 01:33.990
What should we do now?

01:34.250 --> 01:35.780
If we let the rumors spread,

01:35.870 --> 01:38.670
I'm afraid a mutiny
will really happen in the army.

03:06.500 --> 03:10.590
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

03:10.980 --> 03:13.500
[Episode 6]

03:13.570 --> 03:16.100
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

03:17.360 --> 03:19.360
Do you have any idea
what they are saying out there?

03:19.360 --> 03:20.190
They say our Prince Jing'an's family

03:20.190 --> 03:21.900
disregards the lives of Beifu soldiers

03:21.900 --> 03:22.900
and shelters the culprit

03:22.900 --> 03:24.150
to please the noble clans!

03:24.150 --> 03:25.910
If it leads to a mutiny in the army,

03:25.910 --> 03:28.310
can you still be
the Heir of Prince Jing'an?

03:29.500 --> 03:31.310
I know you didn't do it, Yao.

03:31.870 --> 03:32.530
I trust you.

03:33.320 --> 03:34.840
You actually suspected me?

03:34.840 --> 03:35.750
No matter how worked up I am,

03:35.750 --> 03:37.480
I would never be this reckless.

03:38.060 --> 03:40.480
If Prince Jing'an's household
loses the trust of the Beifu soldiers,

03:40.480 --> 03:41.360
what good

03:42.030 --> 03:43.150
would it do for me?

03:47.240 --> 03:48.440
Yao, haven't you held

03:49.490 --> 03:51.680
a lot of grudges
against me all these years?

03:51.680 --> 03:53.990
Yes, that is true.

03:54.630 --> 03:55.490
Over the years,

03:55.630 --> 03:57.030
how many letters have I written you,

03:57.030 --> 03:57.910
asking to join the battle?

03:57.910 --> 03:59.079
You've returned them all

03:59.079 --> 04:00.280
and even sent them back to Mother,

04:00.280 --> 04:01.430
making her watch me every day.

04:01.430 --> 04:01.910
Also...

04:01.910 --> 04:02.680
Also what?

04:05.260 --> 04:05.890
Nothing.

04:08.400 --> 04:09.800
We are talking about you.

04:11.430 --> 04:12.960
If you keep letting this go on,

04:12.960 --> 04:14.690
once you lose the army's trust,

04:15.080 --> 04:17.680
how terrifying would it be
on the battlefield?

04:18.480 --> 04:21.060
You should at least send Xie Jiayu back
to the Grand Tutor's Mansion

04:21.060 --> 04:22.480
to clearly show everyone your attitude.

04:22.480 --> 04:24.410
My attitude has always been clear.

04:25.390 --> 04:26.040
Yao,

04:27.070 --> 04:29.310
Xie Jiayu is not
Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

04:29.310 --> 04:31.360
Whoever says she is
should show the evidence.

04:31.360 --> 04:32.520
There's no need to respond

04:32.520 --> 04:33.590
to these baseless rumors.

04:33.590 --> 04:34.190
You...

04:37.870 --> 04:39.270
That's how it is.

04:40.180 --> 04:42.190
Seems like as long as His Highness
stays in the capital,

04:42.190 --> 04:43.800
the turmoil just won't end.

04:44.680 --> 04:46.280
Someone wants to sow discord

04:46.760 --> 04:49.290
between His Highness
and the Beifu soldiers.

04:51.190 --> 04:53.120
You don't seem to worry about
the dispute between the Empress Dowager

04:53.120 --> 04:54.800
and Prince Jing'an's household.

04:54.800 --> 04:56.330
My concern lies elsewhere.

04:58.030 --> 05:01.090
His Highness is probably
really in love with Xie Jiayu.

05:02.670 --> 05:03.960
You just realized it?

05:05.020 --> 05:07.110
So you knew it earlier but didn't tell me!

05:07.110 --> 05:09.310
That's because I bet that the two of them

05:10.190 --> 05:11.450
won't end up together.

05:11.620 --> 05:12.540
Why?

05:13.160 --> 05:14.310
Xiao Wuyi

05:14.310 --> 05:16.160
always gets whatever he wants.

05:19.420 --> 05:20.240
Really?

05:21.000 --> 05:23.270
Then... Then Jiayu and Prince Qi...

05:23.270 --> 05:23.920
Yeah,

05:24.310 --> 05:25.600
there is nothing Xiao Wuyi

05:25.600 --> 05:26.800
wants but cannot get.

05:27.800 --> 05:29.430
But no matter how much he likes her,

05:29.430 --> 05:30.890
what if he doesn't want it,

05:31.250 --> 05:33.360
or simply doesn't even dare to have it?

05:33.360 --> 05:34.159
You're wrong.

05:34.920 --> 05:37.070
Many things in this world can be given up,

05:37.070 --> 05:38.560
but not love.

05:38.900 --> 05:40.790
How about we make a bet then?

05:41.070 --> 05:41.920
Okay.

05:41.920 --> 05:42.870
You know what?

05:43.159 --> 05:45.680
My husband and I used to bet a lot,

05:46.550 --> 05:47.500
and I never lost.

05:47.940 --> 05:50.140
Then you'll definitely
lose to me this time.

05:50.140 --> 05:51.870
Actually, I forgot to tell you.

05:52.159 --> 05:54.220
I have one more advantage in winning.

06:00.840 --> 06:02.960
Oh, no. Jiayu still doesn't know that

06:02.990 --> 06:04.650
Ziqi isn't Xiao Wuyi's child.

06:04.680 --> 06:06.360
And our relationship with His Highness—

06:06.360 --> 06:07.930
has she not figured it out?

06:08.880 --> 06:10.810
No way, I must go tell her right now.

06:11.630 --> 06:12.390
Calm down.

06:12.950 --> 06:14.290
His Highness didn't ask us
to tell her yet.

06:14.290 --> 06:15.970
What if she misunderstood it?

06:16.000 --> 06:18.630
Then we can enjoy watching His Highness
make a fool of himself.

06:18.630 --> 06:21.040
Don't you want to see that?

06:22.270 --> 06:23.040
I do.

06:23.470 --> 06:26.180
Darling, it's rare for you
to be in the mood

06:26.720 --> 06:28.250
to invite me to such a place.

06:28.920 --> 06:31.070
Fields, shops, and accounts

06:31.480 --> 06:32.210
are all here.

06:32.830 --> 06:35.120
What I brought
from my Princess's Mansion before

06:35.120 --> 06:36.720
and what your Xie family owns

06:37.510 --> 06:39.240
have all been divided clearly.

06:40.800 --> 06:43.530
I've brought
your favorite rice cakes, Darling.

06:43.980 --> 06:45.180
The vendor, Li, said...

06:45.180 --> 06:47.800
I've also told the butler the details
of the daily chores.

06:47.800 --> 06:49.600
Just accept this divorce paper.

06:50.520 --> 06:52.120
[Divorce Agreement]

07:00.040 --> 07:00.870
I don't agree.

07:01.160 --> 07:03.750
Lord Xie, why bother putting on an act?

07:03.950 --> 07:06.720
Darling, we've been married
for 20 years after all.

07:06.720 --> 07:08.520
We've been married for 20 years,

07:08.680 --> 07:10.140
but you've never loved me.

07:11.280 --> 07:13.510
You, Lord Xie, play tricks to gain power

07:14.450 --> 07:16.570
and manipulate people as you like.

07:16.780 --> 07:18.830
You know I'd hold back for fear
of causing collateral damage.

07:18.830 --> 07:20.810
If I exposed Li Mao's true identity,

07:20.810 --> 07:23.870
he would die, and Jiayu would definitely
suffer agony.

07:23.930 --> 07:25.420
So you had nothing to fear.

07:26.140 --> 07:27.310
You knew my temper

07:27.740 --> 07:29.360
and that once the secret was exposed,

07:29.360 --> 07:31.070
my attitude would definitely be like this.

07:31.070 --> 07:32.240
Yet you still did it.

07:32.990 --> 07:34.720
Since you've made your choice,

07:34.820 --> 07:36.620
then I've also made my decision.

07:39.390 --> 07:40.430
At this point,

07:41.070 --> 07:43.330
I'm not asking for your opinion anymore.

07:48.950 --> 07:50.750
But we still have our daughter, Jiayu.

07:50.750 --> 07:53.270
When you plotted for her
to enter Prince Jing'an's Mansion

07:53.270 --> 07:55.680
and for her to use the repeating crossbows
to murder the Beifu soldiers,

07:55.680 --> 07:58.409
did you still remember
that she's your daughter?

08:00.690 --> 08:01.320
Right,

08:02.680 --> 08:04.740
she is not your biological daughter.

08:05.890 --> 08:07.820
But you have doted on her for years.

08:08.770 --> 08:11.300
And she has called you Father
for just as long!

08:11.720 --> 08:12.520
Darling, I...

08:16.950 --> 08:18.470
I also had no other choice.

08:19.260 --> 08:20.410
What I did was

08:20.430 --> 08:22.840
the best choice for the greater good.

08:25.240 --> 08:26.810
For your own selfish desires, you caused

08:26.810 --> 08:29.070
the deaths of 30,000 soldiers
who defended our state.

08:29.070 --> 08:30.600
Was this your best choice?

08:31.220 --> 08:32.750
You, Lord Xie, who once devoted yourself

08:32.750 --> 08:35.480
to the greater good,
followed by scholars all over the world,

08:35.480 --> 08:38.809
have now become the very person
you used to despise the most.

08:39.440 --> 08:40.640
You don't want Jiayu,

08:41.000 --> 08:41.929
but I do want her.

08:42.700 --> 08:44.169
If you feel even the slightest guilt

08:44.169 --> 08:45.320
towards Jiayu or me,

08:46.000 --> 08:47.400
sign this divorce paper,

08:47.910 --> 08:49.960
and from now on, we'll cut ties with you.

08:49.960 --> 08:52.290
Whether you succeed or fail in the future,

08:52.500 --> 08:54.970
Jiayu will only be
the daughter of me, Princess Yunzhao.

08:54.970 --> 08:57.320
You must not force Jiayu
to do anything for you.

08:57.320 --> 09:00.770
Otherwise, I don't mind
bringing you down with me.

09:18.870 --> 09:21.480
Darling, where will you go then?

09:22.550 --> 09:23.630
Jiankang is not the Capital.

09:23.630 --> 09:24.960
There is no Princess's Mansion here.

09:24.960 --> 09:26.080
The world is vast.

09:27.270 --> 09:29.000
Wherever I end up in the future,

09:29.240 --> 09:31.700
it will have nothing
to do with you, Lord Xie.

09:36.360 --> 09:37.200
Xie Huaigui,

09:38.520 --> 09:39.650
I've had no regrets.

09:41.000 --> 09:43.750
I hope you won't regret today either.

09:48.510 --> 09:49.390
Xie Huaigui,

09:49.960 --> 09:51.760
after over 20 years of marriage,

09:52.030 --> 09:54.290
allow me to scheme against you this once.

09:55.150 --> 09:56.950
You want Li Mao to be the Emperor?

09:57.520 --> 09:58.520
No way.

10:04.510 --> 10:06.510
Over 100 years after Ye was founded,

10:06.670 --> 10:08.720
Emperor Wenxi and Empress Wenxi
attempted to reform,

10:08.720 --> 10:10.680
yet it threatened the interests
of noble families.

10:10.680 --> 10:12.230
Northern Qin took the chance
to invade the south,

10:12.230 --> 10:14.150
while the nobles stood by and watched.

10:14.150 --> 10:16.790
Emperor Wenxi died
in battle while leading his troops.

10:16.790 --> 10:18.670
The pregnant Empress Wenxi

10:17.800 --> 10:19.700
[Empress Wenxi]

10:18.870 --> 10:21.030
ordered the imperial family and the nobles
to flee south,

10:21.030 --> 10:22.720
yet she stayed in the Capital alone

10:22.720 --> 10:24.580
to hold off the Northern Qin army,

10:24.840 --> 10:26.500
and eventually died in a fire,

10:27.120 --> 10:28.500
leaving behind the final words—

10:28.500 --> 10:32.700
when the Phoenix Heart Token appears,
peace shall be restored in the world.

10:38.440 --> 10:39.260
You are late.

10:39.870 --> 10:41.140
I rushed here upon hearing

10:41.140 --> 10:42.270
my brother's death.

10:42.360 --> 10:44.080
Any news on the person
I asked you to find?

10:44.080 --> 10:45.340
We've spread the word.

10:46.000 --> 10:47.860
But it has been more than 20 years.

10:48.350 --> 10:50.810
I'm not sure
how many of them are still alive.

10:58.460 --> 10:59.970
Today's medicine is ready.

10:59.970 --> 11:03.430
Madam Ruisheng said I must
watch you finish it, Your Highness.

11:05.600 --> 11:08.360
You have drafted and discarded
the charter for military reform

11:08.360 --> 11:09.390
over and over again.

11:09.390 --> 11:10.990
Can you really figure it out?

11:12.170 --> 11:12.960
What is this?

11:13.960 --> 11:14.890
I almost forgot.

11:15.100 --> 11:16.740
The porter sent this over,

11:16.870 --> 11:18.730
saying it's a letter for Lady Xie.

11:20.670 --> 11:22.340
[Yunzhao]

11:23.790 --> 11:24.950
What is Xie Jiayu doing?

11:24.950 --> 11:26.200
She asked someone to buy osmanthus honey

11:26.200 --> 11:27.670
and is still making hawthorn cakes,

11:27.670 --> 11:30.950
because she dislikes
the sour hawthorn bought a few days ago.

11:30.950 --> 11:33.070
Li Mao will starve to death
if he's seriously waiting

11:33.070 --> 11:35.530
for her hawthorn cakes
to whet his appetite.

11:38.330 --> 11:40.520
No, Your Highness,
take your medicine first,

11:40.520 --> 11:42.650
or Madam Ruisheng will scold us again.

11:45.030 --> 11:46.490
You're blocking my light.

11:52.480 --> 11:54.150
It's so dirty! Go away.

11:54.910 --> 11:55.970
It's sweet enough.

11:57.030 --> 11:57.750
Not enough.

11:57.750 --> 11:59.320
Mao and Lejun like sweets.

12:02.320 --> 12:04.320
So you know their tastes quite well.

12:07.110 --> 12:08.440
What are you doing here?

12:08.750 --> 12:10.560
Don't worry, you don't need to watch me.

12:10.560 --> 12:11.610
I won't run around

12:11.630 --> 12:12.890
and cause you trouble.

12:13.930 --> 12:14.600
I know

12:15.230 --> 12:16.840
some people have been
giving you a hard time recently

12:16.840 --> 12:19.040
over Young Master of Miraculous Craft.

12:20.190 --> 12:20.990
You know that?

12:22.590 --> 12:24.920
Xiao Wuyi, do you really think I'm stupid?

12:27.550 --> 12:28.630
That day at the Conscription Office,

12:28.630 --> 12:30.840
the Commander of the Imperial Guards
made it so clear.

12:30.840 --> 12:31.990
Someone used the storybooks

12:31.990 --> 12:33.510
to claim that I am
Young Master of Miraculous Craft

12:33.510 --> 12:34.970
and harmed the Beifu Army.

12:35.240 --> 12:36.480
If you don't punish me,

12:36.480 --> 12:37.440
someone will put the blame

12:37.440 --> 12:38.300
on you instead.

12:39.000 --> 12:39.860
If I run around,

12:39.930 --> 12:41.440
wouldn't that cause you trouble?

12:41.440 --> 12:43.150
What you said that day was harsh,

12:43.150 --> 12:44.350
but I've understood.

12:46.210 --> 12:46.850
By the way.

12:50.480 --> 12:52.340
This is a letter from your mother.

12:52.360 --> 12:53.320
Put it in the back for me.

12:53.320 --> 12:54.380
I'll read it later.

13:07.030 --> 13:07.840
Xie Jiayu.

13:08.750 --> 13:09.750
What now?

13:13.360 --> 13:14.890
The dusk scenery is lovely.

13:16.200 --> 13:17.440
Go get me a soft couch.

13:18.150 --> 13:19.880
I want to enjoy the sunset here.

13:20.700 --> 13:22.270
Go back to your own courtyard to enjoy it!

13:22.270 --> 13:23.530
I have no time for that.

13:25.670 --> 13:27.820
After the Double Ninth Festival's
sacrificial ritual,

13:27.820 --> 13:29.670
I can arrange a meeting
between you and Li Mao.

13:29.670 --> 13:30.720
Don't you want it?

14:06.320 --> 14:09.720
It'd be great if I could have a cup
of freshly brewed Biluochun

14:10.440 --> 14:11.640
to moisten my throat.

14:13.670 --> 14:16.130
Okay, I'm going to make tea
for you right now.

14:25.390 --> 14:26.390
Don't waste time.

14:35.680 --> 14:37.140
It's getting a bit chilly.

14:37.720 --> 14:38.920
Go get me a robe.

14:39.000 --> 14:41.930
Are you going to let me make
the hawthorn cakes or not?

14:48.000 --> 14:48.740
You've promised

14:48.740 --> 14:50.840
to let me meet Mao
on the Double Ninth Festival, huh?

14:50.840 --> 14:52.040
Why would I lie to you?

14:52.750 --> 14:54.480
Fine, then just boss me around.

14:54.720 --> 14:56.380
Today, whatever you say goes.

15:31.360 --> 15:33.760
And you said you wanted
to watch the sunset?

15:50.760 --> 15:51.950
[Little Xiao Wuyi]

16:02.060 --> 16:03.340
[Little Xiao Yao]

16:02.120 --> 16:03.390
Protect Sheng!

16:06.340 --> 16:07.100
Stop there!

16:10.200 --> 16:10.960
Stop!

16:11.720 --> 16:12.520
Stop running!

16:16.480 --> 16:17.120
Sheng!

16:21.200 --> 16:21.910
Father!

16:22.720 --> 16:23.270
Father!

16:23.440 --> 16:25.040
Take your brother and leave!

16:25.630 --> 16:26.390
Go!

16:30.960 --> 16:31.600
Brother!

16:31.790 --> 16:32.630
Brother!

16:59.200 --> 17:01.930
♪ One glance stirs heart's doom,
near yet far ♪

17:02.150 --> 17:04.700
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

17:06.400 --> 17:10.410
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

17:10.579 --> 17:12.579
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

17:14.540 --> 17:17.540
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

17:17.710 --> 17:22.079
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

17:22.109 --> 17:22.910
It's too sweet.

17:22.910 --> 17:25.819
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

17:26.000 --> 17:27.160
I can't indulge myself in it.

17:26.750 --> 17:29.570
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

17:34.110 --> 17:35.370
Why are you still here?

17:37.680 --> 17:38.480
I just woke up.

17:39.480 --> 17:40.540
Are they for Li Mao?

17:40.790 --> 17:41.400
No.

17:41.830 --> 17:43.350
This plate is for Ziqi.

17:43.750 --> 17:45.350
This piece is for my mother.

17:45.920 --> 17:46.880
And this for Ruisheng;

17:46.880 --> 17:47.810
this for Yuanji.

17:49.070 --> 17:51.530
This last piece is
for the Dowager Princess.

17:52.310 --> 17:54.310
I just made them all while I was at it.

17:57.110 --> 17:58.440
This one is for Lejun.

18:00.560 --> 18:01.800
This one is for Mao.

18:01.830 --> 18:03.160
Don't get them mixed up.

18:05.680 --> 18:06.440
A love poem?

18:07.350 --> 18:08.240
No peeking!

18:08.550 --> 18:10.010
I'm not interested at all.

18:11.110 --> 18:11.830
Oh, right,

18:12.330 --> 18:14.020
you have Yuanji and Ruisheng.

18:14.310 --> 18:15.510
If you were to receive love poems,

18:15.510 --> 18:16.510
you'd get two.

18:21.030 --> 18:21.720
Hold on.

18:28.240 --> 18:29.350
And who is this for?

18:30.370 --> 18:33.170
Thanks for arranging a meeting
between Mao and me.

18:34.680 --> 18:36.610
It's such a shabby thank-you gift.

18:36.720 --> 18:39.720
Take it or leave it.
Return it to me if you don't want it.

18:43.270 --> 18:45.200
I have things to handle at my place.

19:01.000 --> 19:01.800
What's wrong?

19:02.160 --> 19:03.890
The blindness happened again.

19:04.830 --> 19:06.630
It took about 2 hours to recover.

19:08.070 --> 19:09.670
I'll do acupuncture for you.

19:09.830 --> 19:10.960
How much time do I have left?

19:10.960 --> 19:12.720
It is caused by blood stasis in your head.

19:12.720 --> 19:14.510
If we can't find a way
to treat the stasis,

19:14.510 --> 19:15.680
you might survive 3 to 5 years.

19:15.680 --> 19:16.340
Or maybe...

19:20.070 --> 19:20.830
just one day.

19:23.580 --> 19:25.980
We must not let anyone else
know about this.

19:26.240 --> 19:27.110
If anyone asks,

19:27.480 --> 19:29.440
just say
I have an arrow wound on my chest.

19:29.440 --> 19:30.880
This is not a long-term solution.

19:30.880 --> 19:32.940
I, Xiao Wuyi, cannot have a weakness.

19:38.550 --> 19:39.610
Three to five years

19:41.510 --> 19:42.350
are enough.

19:44.880 --> 19:45.640
Don't worry.

19:46.920 --> 19:48.320
I will do everything I can

19:49.310 --> 19:50.160
to find a cure.

20:00.130 --> 20:01.190
What's up, My Lady?

20:02.970 --> 20:05.400
My father and mother are divorced.

20:10.980 --> 20:13.640
This is a decision I made
after long consideration.

20:13.640 --> 20:15.450
But this has nothing to do with you.

20:15.450 --> 20:17.020
You are still our daughter.

20:17.720 --> 20:20.000
Yaoyao, between husband and wife,

20:20.480 --> 20:23.280
besides love,
there should also be understanding

20:23.310 --> 20:24.110
and respect.

20:24.750 --> 20:26.830
They're companions on the journey of life.

20:26.830 --> 20:28.880
I hope you can understand this early,

20:28.880 --> 20:31.110
suffer less from the agony
of love, hate, and partings,

20:31.110 --> 20:32.680
and find peace of mind.

20:33.750 --> 20:34.880
I plan to leave Jiankang

20:34.880 --> 20:36.310
to travel through Ye.

20:36.750 --> 20:38.210
I will be back in a few days.

20:38.640 --> 20:40.240
I will leave letters for you.

20:40.720 --> 20:42.750
Besides, as for your father,

20:43.380 --> 20:44.580
he has his struggles.

20:44.960 --> 20:46.290
Don't blame or hate him,

20:46.920 --> 20:48.920
but don't trust him blindly either.

20:49.200 --> 20:50.200
Keep this in mind.

20:54.160 --> 20:56.160
Who is up ahead, blocking my way?

21:12.300 --> 21:14.120
[Liu Yu'e, senior maid of Empress Wenxi
of the previous dynasty]

21:16.640 --> 21:17.440
It's you?

21:18.440 --> 21:19.370
You're not dead?

21:19.750 --> 21:23.550
Your Highness, you're going to find
Crown Prince Wenxi, aren't you?

21:26.150 --> 21:28.760
[Palace of Eternal Peace]

21:38.440 --> 21:39.370
Hawthorn cakes?

21:40.810 --> 21:42.810
Why did Yaoyao suddenly make these?

21:43.070 --> 21:44.330
I don't like sour food.

21:45.440 --> 21:47.300
I just got something for her to do.

21:47.720 --> 21:49.750
If you don't like them,
I'll throw them away.

21:49.750 --> 21:52.080
I won't let Yaoyao's kindness go to waste.

21:52.470 --> 21:53.730
There's also a letter.

22:00.720 --> 22:02.580
She told me to take care of myself,

22:02.640 --> 22:04.720
said everyone in Prince Jing'an's Mansion
treated her very well,

22:04.720 --> 22:06.050
and told me not to worry.

22:08.030 --> 22:10.720
She also mentioned
that Young Master of Miraculous Craft

22:10.720 --> 22:12.120
has caused a stir lately,

22:12.240 --> 22:15.570
putting both you and the Beifu Army
through a lot of trouble.

22:16.480 --> 22:17.350
She is young.

22:17.550 --> 22:19.160
Sometimes her words are offensive,

22:19.160 --> 22:20.310
but she is kind in nature.

22:20.310 --> 22:21.750
Please bear with her more.

22:21.750 --> 22:23.830
You don't need to worry about Xie Jiayu.

22:23.830 --> 22:26.540
She can mess around as she likes
in Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

22:26.540 --> 22:28.940
The priority right now is
the Double Ninth Festival Ceremony.

22:28.940 --> 22:31.240
The Empress Dowager already made a move
against Young Master of Miraculous Craft,

22:31.240 --> 22:33.300
trying to stir up a mutiny in the army,

22:34.000 --> 22:35.200
so she definitely has

22:35.580 --> 22:37.310
a backup plan for the Ceremony.

22:41.760 --> 22:43.750
These are the hawthorn cakes Yaoyao made.

22:43.750 --> 22:45.080
I saved 2 pieces for you.

22:48.520 --> 22:49.520
It's all my fault,

22:49.800 --> 22:51.440
having dragged you down with me.

22:51.440 --> 22:52.770
You look so haggard now.

22:54.030 --> 22:54.760
Give it a try.

23:00.430 --> 23:01.160
What is this?

23:03.260 --> 23:04.920
Did the Empress Dowager do it?

23:05.920 --> 23:08.140
Her Majesty made me practice calligraphy

23:08.140 --> 23:09.880
and didn't allow me to lower my arms.

23:09.880 --> 23:11.030
If I lowered them,

23:11.420 --> 23:12.950
the needles would prick me.

23:14.190 --> 23:14.830
Brother,

23:15.700 --> 23:16.780
when will this kind

23:17.670 --> 23:20.100
of life ever end?

23:24.660 --> 23:27.490
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

23:27.830 --> 23:29.350
Look at this bow.

23:29.350 --> 23:30.550
You must remember to tighten up

23:30.550 --> 23:31.480
these two spots.

23:31.510 --> 23:33.170
And it must be made of cowhide.

23:33.210 --> 23:34.160
Also...

23:41.120 --> 23:42.180
What are you doing?

23:43.860 --> 23:45.920
I am teaching Da to practice writing.

23:46.800 --> 23:48.110
Mao used to teach him.

23:48.190 --> 23:49.340
Now that Mao is not here,

23:49.340 --> 23:50.140
I have to do it.

23:51.550 --> 23:52.350
Alright, Da.

23:52.420 --> 23:54.150
That's all for today's lesson.

23:54.320 --> 23:56.190
I gave you the copybooks just now.

23:56.350 --> 23:58.210
You must practice hard with them.

24:01.960 --> 24:03.030
I'll go see Da out.

24:06.720 --> 24:07.580
Your Highness.

24:11.850 --> 24:14.230
These are the latest weapon designs
by the Secondary Consort.

24:14.230 --> 24:16.880
They are the standard types
used by the fallen Lieutenant Generals,

24:16.880 --> 24:18.680
but more exquisite and detailed.

24:18.680 --> 24:19.550
She paid a hefty price

24:19.550 --> 24:21.350
and had Da find
the best blacksmith in the city

24:21.350 --> 24:22.680
to rush the production.

24:23.350 --> 24:24.410
Should we stop her?

24:25.480 --> 24:27.070
In the name
of Young Master of Miraculous Craft?

24:27.070 --> 24:28.000
It's anonymous.

24:28.030 --> 24:29.110
Da is mute anyway.

24:29.510 --> 24:30.970
He won't leak it to others.

24:32.380 --> 24:33.380
Then let her do it.

24:41.050 --> 24:42.810
[On the day
of the Double Ninth Festival Ceremony]

25:04.790 --> 25:05.990
Is everything ready?

25:06.340 --> 25:07.400
Everything is set.

25:07.910 --> 25:09.020
At the auspicious hour,

25:09.020 --> 25:11.500
the sacrificial ritual
for the Beifu Army can begin.

25:11.500 --> 25:14.060
Today, you're representing His Majesty.

25:14.270 --> 25:15.310
The civil and military officials

25:15.310 --> 25:18.240
and the people of Jiankang
all have their eyes on you.

25:19.040 --> 25:21.640
I will bear your instructions in mind,
Your Majesty,

25:21.640 --> 25:24.440
and will certainly not
lose the imperial dignity.

25:27.110 --> 25:29.480
If His Majesty weren't
in such poor health,

25:29.480 --> 25:30.880
it wouldn't be your turn.

25:33.030 --> 25:33.750
Alright.

25:35.030 --> 25:35.830
You may leave.

25:45.270 --> 25:48.890
Your Majesty,
His Highness seems quite obedient.

25:49.240 --> 25:50.570
The more obedient he is,

25:51.350 --> 25:53.480
the harder it is
for the resentment in my heart

25:53.480 --> 25:54.590
to fade.

25:56.720 --> 25:58.520
I have fought for half a century.

25:58.920 --> 26:01.120
Did I just pave the way for someone else?

26:03.000 --> 26:05.830
How is the preparation of the weapons

26:06.200 --> 26:07.460
designed by Xie Jiayu?

26:07.510 --> 26:09.510
They have been rushed to completion.

26:09.510 --> 26:10.270
Very well.

26:11.990 --> 26:13.890
Then let's wait and watch
tonight's great show

26:13.890 --> 26:16.720
of discord
between the Beifu soldiers and generals.

26:16.720 --> 26:17.980
Let's see how Xiao Wuyi

26:18.440 --> 26:19.570
will handle it.

26:21.750 --> 26:22.550
Belt.

26:29.070 --> 26:29.720
Sword.

26:35.200 --> 26:36.600
Couldn't you get them yourself?

26:36.600 --> 26:37.320
Man.

26:46.160 --> 26:47.390
The Double Ninth
sacrificial ritual tonight

26:47.390 --> 26:48.320
will be crowded.

26:48.350 --> 26:49.350
Don't run around.

26:49.440 --> 26:50.040
Remember,

26:50.960 --> 26:52.620
once you step out of this room,

26:52.920 --> 26:54.400
you'll no longer be Xie Jiayu.

26:54.400 --> 26:55.550
Your name is Qing Long.

26:55.550 --> 26:56.550
I know.

26:56.960 --> 26:59.160
Today I am Young Lord Xiao's bodyguard,

26:59.240 --> 26:59.960
Qing Long.

27:01.200 --> 27:02.160
Then how should you address me?

27:02.160 --> 27:02.790
Xiao Wu...

27:05.830 --> 27:06.760
Your Highness.

27:08.480 --> 27:09.270
And then?

27:13.030 --> 27:15.440
I'm at your command
whenever you need anything, Your Highness.

27:15.440 --> 27:17.640
I am willing to lay down my life for you,

27:17.790 --> 27:19.430
come what may, Your Highness!

27:19.430 --> 27:21.560
Am I usually this much of a bootlicker?

27:26.790 --> 27:28.320
We should put on a full show.

27:28.550 --> 27:29.610
Give me your sword.

27:32.550 --> 27:33.240
Hurry.

27:41.920 --> 27:43.180
Your suit looks great.

27:43.270 --> 27:44.400
Give it to me as well.

27:46.090 --> 27:48.290
Why do I have to be the one
to be replaced?

27:51.000 --> 27:51.600
Come here.

27:51.880 --> 27:53.010
Let go of me, Yan Yue!

27:53.030 --> 27:54.190
Are you even a woman?

27:57.070 --> 27:58.070
Stop right there!

28:00.550 --> 28:03.880
I, Qing Long, will definitely
keep you safe, Your Highness.

28:04.140 --> 28:05.740
Where are Father and Mother?

28:06.020 --> 28:07.610
Father is going to play leaf cards.

28:07.610 --> 28:09.870
Mother said she's not into festivities.

28:10.200 --> 28:11.720
Double Ninth is to honor the elderly.

28:11.720 --> 28:13.450
How can these two elders not go?

28:13.490 --> 28:14.360
No way.

28:14.650 --> 28:15.750
I'll go get Mother with us.

28:15.750 --> 28:17.260
If Mother doesn't want to go,

28:17.260 --> 28:18.590
we shouldn't force her.

28:19.070 --> 28:20.160
It's crowded tonight.

28:20.160 --> 28:21.550
We can just

28:21.550 --> 28:23.480
bring Mother several pots
of chrysanthemum wine.

28:23.480 --> 28:26.000
Mother, let's go.

28:26.030 --> 28:27.470
I want to see the lanterns,

28:27.470 --> 28:29.420
buy sugar figures, and ride a boat.

28:29.600 --> 28:30.930
You have so many wishes.

28:31.160 --> 28:32.400
Did you practice acupuncture today?

28:32.400 --> 28:34.060
How many poems did you recite?

28:34.240 --> 28:36.400
There will be a large crowd
in front of Shenwu Gate today.

28:36.400 --> 28:37.400
Make sure to watch Ziqi closely.

28:37.400 --> 28:38.440
Don't let him run around.

28:38.440 --> 28:40.570
Remember, you must return before 7 PM.

28:40.790 --> 28:43.310
He must be in bed by 7 PM.

28:43.820 --> 28:45.990
That's too early.

28:47.750 --> 28:49.120
If you don't behave well tonight,

28:49.120 --> 28:50.920
what I promised you won't count.

28:51.110 --> 28:52.070
Father,

28:52.240 --> 28:52.970
don't worry.

28:53.080 --> 28:54.600
I'll be good and won't run around.

28:54.600 --> 28:58.260
You promised to take me horseback riding
in the northern suburbs.

28:58.790 --> 28:59.850
It's getting late.

28:59.880 --> 29:00.880
Where is Jiayu?

29:02.400 --> 29:02.960
Her?

29:03.680 --> 29:04.720
Good thing she didn't come.

29:04.720 --> 29:05.720
Forget about her.

29:05.780 --> 29:08.110
At least she won't cause me trouble again.

29:31.750 --> 29:33.160
I heard that today they were specifically

29:33.160 --> 29:36.620
erecting a monument
for the 30,000 soldiers of the Beifu Army.

29:39.840 --> 29:42.870
[Monument of Loyalty]

29:51.030 --> 29:52.030
Who are you again?

29:52.790 --> 29:53.420
Qing Long.

29:53.750 --> 29:54.950
Then stand straight.

30:02.300 --> 30:03.500
Is everything ready?

30:03.600 --> 30:05.330
Everything has been arranged.

30:06.440 --> 30:07.240
Let's begin.

30:47.920 --> 30:49.320
By His Majesty's decree.

31:09.270 --> 31:10.130
Your Highness.

31:14.720 --> 31:16.470
In the Battle of Jiuzhang Plain,

31:16.470 --> 31:18.400
the Beifu Army destroyed the enemy

31:18.640 --> 31:19.960
and brought peace.

31:20.750 --> 31:22.950
They defended the land with their lives

31:23.510 --> 31:25.040
and achieved great merits.

31:25.270 --> 31:26.590
Today is the Double Ninth Festival.

31:26.590 --> 31:29.350
We've erected the Monument of Loyalty
before Shenwu Gate

31:29.350 --> 31:31.410
to honor heaven, earth, and spirits,

31:31.480 --> 31:32.880
hoping those loyal souls

31:34.270 --> 31:35.920
can return to their homeland.

31:35.920 --> 31:37.720
This is also to express my grief.

31:41.000 --> 31:43.960
Wish His Majesty good health.

31:44.320 --> 31:46.050
May the empire endure forever.

31:46.370 --> 31:48.930
May the 30,000 heroic souls above

31:49.310 --> 31:50.940
bless Ye!

31:55.350 --> 31:56.880
It's a day to climb high, admire

31:56.880 --> 31:58.750
chrysanthemums,
and pray with 1,000 lanterns.

31:58.750 --> 32:01.240
Today, I rejoice with you all.

32:01.720 --> 32:03.180
Thank you, Your Highness.

32:23.310 --> 32:26.640
The entertainment and lantern festivities
will begin shortly.

32:26.640 --> 32:28.070
Wait here with Yan Yue.

32:28.330 --> 32:29.590
I'll go get Li Mao here.

32:42.880 --> 32:44.340
Greetings, Your Majesty.

32:46.440 --> 32:49.440
Is the Beifu Army happy today?

32:49.960 --> 32:51.570
The souls return to their homeland,

32:51.570 --> 32:53.370
and grief lingers in our hearts.

32:53.430 --> 32:55.630
Piles of bones for the sake of the world.

32:56.350 --> 32:57.640
What is there to be happy about?

32:57.640 --> 32:58.400
It seems that

32:59.000 --> 33:00.510
you, Young Lord Xiao, still

33:00.510 --> 33:01.910
hold a grudge against me.

33:02.640 --> 33:03.270
I dare not.

33:04.240 --> 33:07.040
I'm here to borrow someone from you,
Your Majesty.

33:07.270 --> 33:08.070
Who?

33:09.350 --> 33:10.750
His Highness, Prince Qi.

33:13.880 --> 33:14.560
For what?

33:14.590 --> 33:15.450
To have a drink.

33:15.960 --> 33:17.070
It's a day for climbing high,

33:17.070 --> 33:18.400
drinking, and admiring chrysanthemums.

33:18.400 --> 33:19.720
We should celebrate with the people.

33:19.720 --> 33:20.750
The Beifu generals and I

33:20.750 --> 33:22.830
have set up a banquet at Jinguan Pavilion,

33:22.830 --> 33:25.290
waiting for Prince Qi
to join us in drinking,

33:25.960 --> 33:28.890
to show harmony
between the ruler and subordinates.

33:34.960 --> 33:38.270
You're using harmony between the ruler
and subordinates as a reason.

33:38.270 --> 33:39.440
If I don't agree,

33:39.640 --> 33:42.370
wouldn't it equal causing discord
between them?

33:44.680 --> 33:45.030
I...

33:45.030 --> 33:45.690
Never mind.

33:46.720 --> 33:48.450
You may go with Young Lord Xiao.

33:48.480 --> 33:51.140
I wouldn't dare to take the blame
for the discord

33:51.160 --> 33:53.220
between the ruler and subordinates.

33:53.480 --> 33:54.540
Yes, Your Majesty.

33:54.860 --> 33:57.060
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

34:11.280 --> 34:13.550
Do you think His Highness is

34:14.070 --> 34:15.880
going to seek harmony

34:15.880 --> 34:17.739
with the Beifu soldiers tonight,

34:19.500 --> 34:20.290
or going to find

34:20.290 --> 34:22.290
Xiao Wuyi's Secondary Consort?

34:24.199 --> 34:25.120
Your Majesty,

34:25.440 --> 34:28.500
my brother wouldn't dare
to deceive you, Your Majesty.

34:29.139 --> 34:31.540
Tonight, I actually
want him to deceive me.

34:31.960 --> 34:32.960
His Highness and the minister's consort

34:32.960 --> 34:35.590
being both assassinated
at the Double Ninth Lantern Fair,

34:35.590 --> 34:38.670
a death like this would also
go down in history.

34:41.040 --> 34:44.699
What do you think Xiao Wuyi's expression
will be when he finds out?

34:44.739 --> 34:46.670
It will surely be with mixed feelings

34:46.670 --> 34:47.929
and very interesting.

34:55.150 --> 34:55.550
Wuyi.

34:55.550 --> 34:56.750
You even got changed?

34:58.550 --> 34:59.410
Where is Jiayu?

35:00.280 --> 35:01.350
There were too many people just now.

35:01.350 --> 35:02.430
I didn't even see you guys.

35:02.430 --> 35:04.480
You really prefer your love over friends.

35:04.480 --> 35:06.030
I got you
out of the Empress Dowager's hands,

35:06.030 --> 35:07.890
and you didn't even say thank you.

35:08.320 --> 35:08.880
Thanks.

35:09.590 --> 35:10.150
Save it.

35:11.070 --> 35:12.960
I took a risk
to let you two meet this time.

35:12.960 --> 35:14.150
Whether to stay or leave,

35:14.150 --> 35:15.610
you must make up your mind.

35:15.670 --> 35:16.400
I got it.

35:19.930 --> 35:21.660
Your Highness. Your Highness.

35:22.730 --> 35:24.760
We are here to protect you, Your Highness.

35:24.760 --> 35:25.710
Protect me?

35:35.070 --> 35:36.230
Mao, let's go.

35:37.510 --> 35:38.570
Thanks, Xiao Wuyi.

35:38.760 --> 35:39.360
We're off.

35:44.400 --> 35:44.960
Let's go.

35:51.550 --> 35:52.920
Xiao Wuyi!

36:17.510 --> 36:18.910
Yuanji, Madam Ruisheng.

36:19.840 --> 36:20.640
What's wrong?

36:21.280 --> 36:22.440
Something is fishy tonight.

36:22.440 --> 36:24.480
Something serious is going to happen
at the Double Ninth Ceremony.

36:24.480 --> 36:25.450
Something serious?

36:25.450 --> 36:27.510
Many people here are
from military households,

36:27.510 --> 36:28.990
hiding among the commoners.

36:28.990 --> 36:31.250
I bet something big will happen tonight.

36:31.550 --> 36:34.440
His Highness said we must return
to the Mansion before 7 PM.

36:34.440 --> 36:35.830
Did he prepare for this in advance?

36:35.830 --> 36:37.430
Where did this brat go again?

36:37.590 --> 36:38.710
You go back to the Mansion first.

36:38.710 --> 36:39.510
I'll go find him.

36:39.510 --> 36:40.710
Yao, you have trouble walking.

36:40.710 --> 36:42.150
So why don't you go with us?

36:42.150 --> 36:43.350
You guys leave first.

36:44.920 --> 36:46.120
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

36:58.190 --> 36:59.520
Does it look like a fish?

36:59.700 --> 37:00.820
It looks a bit like a pig.

37:00.820 --> 37:02.620
Sir, please make me another one.

37:02.730 --> 37:03.400
Alright, alright.

37:03.400 --> 37:05.000
-Thank you, sir.
-Thank you.

37:09.360 --> 37:12.090
Her Majesty has really
put a lot of effort into it.

37:12.670 --> 37:14.200
What is she going to do next?

37:19.670 --> 37:22.670
Your Majesty, please help me get justice.

37:22.960 --> 37:24.550
I was beaten up by Xiao Wuyi.

37:24.550 --> 37:25.190
You idiot.

37:26.070 --> 37:27.510
Did you catch the person who hit you?

37:27.510 --> 37:28.440
N-No.

37:28.880 --> 37:29.760
If you didn't catch anyone,

37:29.760 --> 37:31.070
how can I help you get justice?

37:31.070 --> 37:32.360
You good-for-nothing.

37:32.360 --> 37:33.360
Bear it yourself.

37:40.030 --> 37:40.880
It seems that

37:42.230 --> 37:43.510
they failed, too.

37:54.550 --> 37:56.880
Since it is
the Double Ninth Festival today,

37:56.880 --> 37:57.760
you don't need to stay here

37:57.760 --> 37:59.290
to keep an old woman like me company.

37:59.290 --> 38:01.750
You must be bored stiff
in the palace lately.

38:01.760 --> 38:02.890
Go and have some fun.

38:04.280 --> 38:05.210
Your Majesty...

38:06.400 --> 38:07.920
Please show mercy, Your Majesty.

38:07.920 --> 38:09.320
Have you thought through

38:09.360 --> 38:10.490
what I said just now?

38:11.510 --> 38:14.440
Will you choose your older brother
or Xie Jiayu?

38:21.030 --> 38:21.760
Yaoyao.

38:23.630 --> 38:26.160
Don't you want to ask me
why I broke my promise?

38:27.320 --> 38:28.920
Why didn't I show up on the day

38:29.000 --> 38:30.230
of our appointment?

38:32.120 --> 38:34.370
Xiao Wuyi and my father both told me that

38:34.880 --> 38:36.140
you did it for the world

38:36.150 --> 38:37.810
and for the peace of Jiankang.

38:38.190 --> 38:38.760
Mao,

38:39.440 --> 38:41.920
let's not talk about this today, okay?

38:47.360 --> 38:48.890
Let's make prayer tablets.

39:09.040 --> 39:11.360
[May Xie Jiayu
be safe and well every year.]

39:12.440 --> 39:14.070
Why do you only wish me safe and well?

39:14.070 --> 39:15.730
Being safe and well is enough.

39:16.760 --> 39:17.620
In the old days,

39:18.400 --> 39:21.150
you'd always write some sentimental poems
that I couldn't understand.

39:21.150 --> 39:23.280
Then I would sell them for a good price.

39:23.820 --> 39:25.480
And we would buy wine to drink.

39:25.730 --> 39:26.860
Lejun and we would

39:27.320 --> 39:29.480
sit on the roof
of Prince Qi's Mansion together,

39:29.480 --> 39:31.740
watching the myriad lights of Jiankang.

39:32.000 --> 39:35.070
How did everything change so suddenly?

39:38.840 --> 39:40.710
Well, that is all in the past.

39:41.550 --> 39:43.410
Let's go hang the prayer tablets.

39:49.030 --> 39:50.150
I'll hang mine here.

39:50.150 --> 39:50.840
Okay.

39:59.820 --> 40:00.660
[He Yuanji, Pei Runheng]

40:00.030 --> 40:02.880
He Yuanji... Pei Runheng?

40:00.660 --> 40:01.510
[The pure radiance remains as before,
engraved in my mind.]

40:04.800 --> 40:07.880
Yu Ruisheng, Duan Qichang, Duan Ziqi?

40:06.350 --> 40:07.020
[Yu Ruisheng, Duan Qichang, Duan Ziqi]

40:07.020 --> 40:07.690
[With jade-like longing,
love is etched upon my heart.]

40:09.070 --> 40:10.000
Oh, my God.

40:10.800 --> 40:11.880
So that's how it is.

40:12.480 --> 40:13.070
I once thought

40:13.070 --> 40:14.990
that our forced separation was
already the greatest misfortune.

40:14.990 --> 40:16.840
I didn't expect Xiao Wuyi
to be even more miserable.

40:16.840 --> 40:19.300
Ruisheng and Yuanji both
love someone else.

40:21.920 --> 40:22.760
Duan Ziqi?

40:23.530 --> 40:24.640
No way...

40:25.090 --> 40:27.350
Ziqi isn't his biological child either!

40:28.280 --> 40:29.110
Hurry, hurry.

40:29.200 --> 40:30.960
Let me hide
these two prayer tablets deeper inside.

40:30.960 --> 40:32.470
Xiao Wuyi cares so much
about his reputation.

40:32.470 --> 40:33.480
He definitely wouldn't want others

40:33.480 --> 40:35.480
to know such an embarrassing thing.

40:35.880 --> 40:37.940
Mao, don't leak it to him, no matter what.

40:37.940 --> 40:40.000
We can't hit Xiao Wuyi where it hurts.

40:40.670 --> 40:41.400
Let's go now.

40:42.230 --> 40:42.920
Jiayu.

40:43.800 --> 40:45.660
Look at this little fish I bought.

40:46.020 --> 40:47.280
What do you think? Do you like it?

40:47.280 --> 40:48.230
It's really nice.

40:48.230 --> 40:49.960
I think it suits you perfectly.

41:02.670 --> 41:05.470
Thanks for arranging a meeting
between Mao and me.

41:16.800 --> 41:17.730
Do you want some?

41:19.960 --> 41:21.020
You can have it all.

41:25.190 --> 41:26.000
It's so good.

41:26.810 --> 41:27.810
Don't you like it?

41:29.360 --> 41:30.510
Of course I do.

41:33.250 --> 41:34.980
But no matter how much I like it,

41:35.000 --> 41:35.930
if it's not mine,

41:37.550 --> 41:38.680
I just can't have it.

41:38.840 --> 41:39.880
It's not yours?

41:41.030 --> 41:43.000
Then can I eat it?

41:59.670 --> 42:00.600
Young Lord Xiao.

42:02.230 --> 42:04.160
Where are you going in such a hurry?

42:04.510 --> 42:07.150
I just haven't seen Jiayu in a long time.

42:08.030 --> 42:10.660
The Empress Dowager told you to lead
Xie Jiayu to the Monument of Loyalty,

42:10.660 --> 42:11.180
right?

42:12.960 --> 42:15.550
Since Xiao Wuyi doesn't want to go back
to the Northern Border,

42:15.550 --> 42:17.190
he will never have to.

42:17.440 --> 42:20.020
When your brother
ascends the throne in the future,

42:20.020 --> 42:21.010
do you think he could tolerate

42:21.010 --> 42:23.010
a powerful minister like Xiao Wuyi?

42:24.030 --> 42:25.030
Think carefully

42:25.760 --> 42:27.230
whether you'll help me

42:27.480 --> 42:28.440
and your brother

42:28.980 --> 42:30.580
get rid of this threat today.

42:32.670 --> 42:34.590
All you have to do is lure Xie Jiayu

42:35.400 --> 42:36.860
to the Monument of Loyalty

42:37.440 --> 42:39.440
at a quarter past 7.

42:40.150 --> 42:43.190
If Xie Jiayu learns
that you're trying to harm her today,

42:43.190 --> 42:44.590
what would she think?

42:46.800 --> 42:47.400
Sorry, excuse me.

42:47.400 --> 42:48.530
Be careful, Yaoyao.

42:56.150 --> 42:58.230
He's the fake Xiao Sheng
who bought the repeating crossbow!

42:58.230 --> 42:58.840
It's that swindler!

42:58.840 --> 42:59.440
Yaoyao!

43:01.990 --> 43:02.920
We did it, Your Majesty.

43:02.920 --> 43:04.480
Xie Jiayu took the bait.

43:05.510 --> 43:06.320
Stop there!
